title: Person of Interest -  Reese at a single CIA mission (Flashback S3E10)
author: AshanayWoW
comment: Dang, the lighting in this scene makes John's face look like a skull, like if he was the angel of death, brilliant!
John is the perfect Batman that we need and deserve but we never got.

Thumbs-Up #128 I am, Monday’s evening 21 January 2019!  I knew a man like him many years ago. Really nice guy. I liked him. He came in, partied with the partiers for several months, gathered names and was packed up and flown out of the European Theater to parts unknown. I liked his style, alot. His name was not even his own.
